(249, 62, 'question', 'What to bring?'),
(250, 62, '_question', 'field_5317c0320ed99'),
(251, 62, 'answer', '<p dir="ltr">Only what you will take running with you. Your running guide will have a hip bag that can carry keys/cards only.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Sydney is blessed with a temperate climate, so most of the year shorts and a shirt/singlet is usually ideal. You’ll warm up while running, usually it feels 10-15 ‘C warmer than if you weren''t running. Apart from a good pair of running shoes, some other things to consider are:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li dir="ltr">\r\n<p dir="ltr">Hat, sunglasses, sunscreen</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir="ltr">\r\n<p dir="ltr">GPS watch or phone with tracking software.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir="ltr">\r\n<p dir="ltr">Camera to take photos along the way.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir="ltr">\r\n<p dir="ltr">Water bottle to carry (although there are often water fountains along the way that your guide will point out).</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir="ltr">Money for coffee or breakfast after the tour.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(252, 62, '_answer', 'field_5317c0440ed9a'),
(253, 61, 'question', 'What to bring?'),
(254, 61, '_question', 'field_5317c0320ed99'),
(255, 61, 'answer', '<p dir="ltr">Only what you will take running with you. Your running guide will have a hip bag that can carry keys/cards only.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Sydney is blessed with a temperate climate, so most of the year shorts and a shirt/singlet is usually ideal. You’ll warm up while running, usually it feels 10-15 ‘C warmer than if you weren''t running. Apart from a good pair of running shoes, some other things to consider are:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li dir="ltr">\r\n<p dir="ltr">Hat, sunglasses, sunscreen</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir="ltr">\r\n<p dir="ltr">GPS watch or phone with tracking software.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir="ltr">\r\n<p dir="ltr">Camera to take photos along the way.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir="ltr">\r\n<p dir="ltr">Water bottle to carry (although there are often water fountains along the way that your guide will point out).</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir="ltr">Money for coffee or breakfast after the tour.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(256, 61, '_answer', 'field_5317c0440ed9a'),
(257, 63, '_edit_last', '1'),
(258, 63, '_edit_lock', '1394065562:1'),
(259, 64, 'question', 'What if it rains?'),
(260, 64, '_question', 'field_5317c0320ed99'),
(261, 64, 'answer', 'Usually runs will still go ahead in rainy conditions. However, in the case of extreme weather conditions or major unforeseen circumstances, we will not run. Your safety is our first priority. If this occurs we will issue a cancellation notice 2 hours prior to departure. Notice of cancellation will be provided via the communication details provided at time of booking.'),
(262, 64, '_answer', 'field_5317c0440ed9a'),
(263, 63, 'question', 'What if it rains?'),
